<content>
    <para id="id6060724">Within the main group (s- and p-block) elements of the Periodic Table (<link target-id="id5055553"/>) there are some general trends that we can observe for the elemental form, as well as the hydrides, oxides, and halides. </para>
    <figure id="id5055553"><media id="id5055553_media" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/jpg" src="../../media/Fig1-dc1b.jpg" id="id5055553__onlineimage" width="400" print-width="3in"/>
